  "key_strengths": [
    "Six gap-to-design patterns (evidence-completion, mechanism-resolution, cell-state/context-mapping, translation-bridge, causality-upgrade, population/stage-specific) cover all major gap types",
    "Gap-to-design dependency map preserves the reasoning chain from identified gap to study design",
    "Prohibition on replacing topic-specific gap with generic workflow prevents generic output",
